# BMAD Document Tools

## Shard Document
Read `_bmad/core/tasks/shard-doc.xml` and follow all instructions. Splits large markdown docs into smaller files by sections.

## Index Docs
Read `_bmad/core/tasks/index-docs.xml` and follow all instructions. Creates lightweight index for quick LLM scanning.
